rows.label: tlk42100149_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Salvaging isn't very big in Invidia,
so things brought in from Avaritia are
very popular, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100149_01_msg0002
rows.name:
On the other hand, in Superbia, people aren't interested
in salvaged goods. Food is more popular, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100149_01_msg0003
rows.name:
For the Avaritia Trade Guild, which can travel freely
between countries, it doesn't matter whether it's Invidia
or Superbia, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100149_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Putting on a good face for both sides for the sake of money...
This is what Chairman Bahn taught me, mo!
